Data Factories
AZURE DATA FACTORY(ADF)
ETL - Extract,transform and load or ELT
azure databricks(ADB) - transformation
ADF - data orchestration
ADF components : 
Integration runtime (IR)- server level
Linked services - Path or location of file
Datasets - acces file
IR types:
Azure auto resolved (default) - if hosted on azure service
self hosted - on premise (when we're on a virtual environment,not on cloud)
Azure SSIS - SQL server intergration system (to run existing SSIS package on azure)
